<i>noun</i>: 작살 [작쌀] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>작살 [작쌀]</dt><br>
<dd>1. shattering; smashing; being smashed</dd><br>
<dd>완전히 깨어지거나 부서짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of having been completely broken.</dd><br>
<dd>2. being destroyed; being ruined</dd><br>
<dd>아주 망가져 손을 쓸 수 없게 되거나 거덜이 남.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which something has been damaged to an irreparable degree or has collapsed.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>